130
00:09:00,863 --> 00:09:02,440
Might be hard to find one now.

131
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:04,010
It's okay, ma'am.

132
00:09:04,223 --> 00:09:05,316
Wait for me a bit.

133
00:09:05,883 --> 00:09:06,883
Go.

134
00:09:23,322 --> 00:09:24,995
