207
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:20,040
Please trust me, Ms. Ramphoei.

208
00:15:20,477 --> 00:15:21,563
Stay here.

209
00:15:21,837 --> 00:15:22,920
Do nothing.

210
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:29,520
