my brother would die this way.

211
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:32,120
Who would be so cruel and do that?

212
00:15:36,107 --> 00:15:38,280
No one could predict this.

213
00:15:40,137 --> 00:15:43,537
Please ease your mind.
Don't worry about anything, ma'am.

214
00:15:44,570 --> 00:15:46,360
My brother's dead now.

215
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,750
I'm all alone now, Dech.

216
00:15:54,850 --> 00:15:56,680
I'll take care of you.

217
00:15:57,097 --> 00:15:58,520
Don't worry, ma'am.

218
00:15:58,903 --> 00:16:01,080
All I ask is
don't look at his body

219
00:16:01,677 --> 00:16:03,800
or do anything
having to do with him.

220
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:07,880
