The servants here insisted that

229
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,880
no one was sent to our house.

230
00:16:51,423 --> 00:16:54,703
It was probably someone's plan
to get you out of the house.

231
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,583
You mean Ramphoei?

232
00:17:01,073 --> 00:17:02,553
Why would she do that?

233
00:17:04,637 --> 00:17:06,737
You know how she is.

234
00:17:07,936 --> 00:17:09,400
