you fell victim to this atrocity.

540
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:30,800
Forget it.

541
00:38:31,173 --> 00:38:32,513
It's nothing, right?

542
00:38:32,653 --> 00:38:34,200
It's not nothing, Fueang!

543
00:38:34,473 --> 00:38:36,040
The viscount raped you!

544
00:38:43,450 --> 00:38:44,403
You son of a bitch.

545
00:38:44,414 --> 00:38:45,747
Fueang is like my sister

546
00:38:45,758 --> 00:38:46,920
but you didn't spare her.

547
00:38:47,094 --> 00:38:49,557
I once regretted doing this to you

548
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,560
because you'd fostered me.

549
00:38:51,877 --> 00:38:53,157
An animal like you

550
00:38:53,262 --> 00:38:56,049
deserves this suffering
as punishment.

551
00:39:11,897 --> 00:39:13,320
How did I get here?

552
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:17,640
My baby.

553
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:19,790
Your baby's okay.

554
00:39:20,217 --> 00:39:21,217
You should rest.

555
00:39:24,396 --> 00:39:26,428
I called a doctor
while you were unconscious.

556
00:39:26,543 --> 00:39:28,543
He said you and the baby were okay.

557
00:39:29,523 --> 00:39:31,523
Will you lie down now, huh?

558
00:39:44,643 --> 00:39:47,363
If you don't believe me,
I'll get the doctor here tomorrow.

559
00:39:47,570 --> 00:39:49,080
I'm not worried about that.

560
00:39:49,650 --> 00:39:51,440
If you're not worried
about the baby,

561
00:39:52,477 --> 00:39:53,760
what are you worried about?

562
00:39:56,543 --> 00:39:58,000
I'm worried about Ms. Malai.

563
00:40:04,863 --> 00:40:07,000
I don't want
you and Ms. Malai to fight.

564
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:08,520
Thanks a lot.

565
00:40:10,403 --> 00:40:12,360
But I have my reason
for not telling her yet.

566
00:40:13,237 --> 00:40:14,320
What do you mean?

567
00:40:15,597 --> 00:40:16,597
I...

568
00:40:25,983 --> 00:40:28,017
I'm worried about
your and your baby's safety.

569
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:34,103
Why are you worried about me?

570
00:40:34,790 --> 00:40:37,480
I'm worried you'll be
in hot water with Ms. Malai.

571
00:40:37,783 --> 00:40:40,400
Fueang, listen to me carefully.

572
00:40:40,770 --> 00:40:44,040
If Ms. Ramphoei finds out
the baby is the viscount's,

573
00:40:44,570 --> 00:40:46,120
she'll try to get rid of you.

574
00:40:46,963 --> 00:40:48,010
You're right.

575
00:40:48,477 --> 00:40:50,190
Even though I don't want his money,

576
00:40:51,663 --> 00:40:52,890
this baby

577
00:40:53,577 --> 00:40:55,577
is the viscount's sole heir.

578
00:40:57,856 --> 00:40:59,237
Don't you trust Ms. Malai?

579
00:40:59,537 --> 00:41:00,537
It's not that.

580
00:41:01,543 --> 00:41:05,240
You know Ms. Malai is the only one
in this house you and I can trust.

581
00:41:05,990 --> 00:41:07,560
Even with Uan and Kam,

582
00:41:07,857 --> 00:41:09,404
you can't slip up about this.

583
00:41:12,663 --> 00:41:13,663
Mm.

584
00:41:14,270 --> 00:41:15,750
When will you tell Ms. Malai?

585
00:41:16,977 --> 00:41:18,840
I've been meaning to tell her,

586
00:41:19,149 --> 00:41:20,363
but I haven't got a chance.

587
00:41:23,037 --> 00:41:24,037
Go back to sleep.

588
00:41:26,450 --> 00:41:27,450
Dech?

589
00:41:27,683 --> 00:41:28,683
Thanks.

590
00:41:28,870 --> 00:41:29,870
Mm.

591
00:41:44,996 --> 00:41:45,996
Come here.

592
00:41:51,309 --> 00:41:53,356
I didn't really want to touch you.

593
00:41:55,089 --> 00:41:56,400
Why did you bring me here?

594
00:41:57,803 --> 00:42:00,080
I'm bothered not getting
to hear the rest of it?

595
00:42:00,603 --> 00:42:01,603
Jeez.

596
00:42:01,763 --> 00:42:03,680
In front of him
you act all trusting,

597
00:42:03,850 --> 00:42:05,040
so lovey-dovey.

598
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:06,920
In reality you're jealous too.

599
00:42:07,210 --> 00:42:08,480
You came just to say this?

600
00:42:08,837 --> 00:42:09,837
So I can leave.

601
00:42:10,523 --> 00:42:12,200
You're not sure either, aren't you?

602
00:42:12,930 --> 00:42:14,800
That Fueang's baby

603
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,030
is not Dech's.

604
00:42:23,390 --> 00:42:24,720
I'm so curious

605
00:42:24,997 --> 00:42:27,417
how much longer
you can act like a saint

606
00:42:28,010 --> 00:42:31,200
when you know
the man you worship so much

607
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:33,760
knocked up another woman.

608
00:42:34,477 --> 00:42:36,124
You can say whatever you want.

609
00:42:37,350 --> 00:42:40,440
But I believe Dech and Fueang
wouldn't lie to me.

610
00:42:44,170 --> 00:42:46,336
I'll wait for the day
that baby's born

611
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:47,997
and it looks like its father.

612
00:42:48,743 --> 00:42:49,840
On that day,

613
00:42:49,970 --> 00:42:52,160
I will laugh so hard I'll
I knock my teeth out.

614
00:42:59,837 --> 00:43:00,837
Oh.

615
00:43:01,830 --> 00:43:03,640
Even if you can accept this,

616
00:43:04,657 --> 00:43:06,657
I will never let her child

617
00:43:06,977 --> 00:43:10,080
get even one penny
from my son's fortune.

618
00:43:47,763 --> 00:43:49,480
Why did Dech tell
two different stories?

619
00:43:50,890 --> 00:43:51,930
I'm not afraid.

620
00:43:52,217 --> 00:43:54,040
Don't think I'm not onto you.

621
00:43:54,317 --> 00:43:55,680
You and Ramphoei

622
00:43:55,990 --> 00:43:57,880
conspired
to paralyze His Lordship.

623
00:43:58,757 --> 00:44:01,657
The same way
you conspired to fake her death!

624
00:44:02,803 --> 00:44:04,000
Don't trust Dech!

625
00:44:05,070 --> 00:44:06,070
Don't trust Dech?

626
00:44:22,841 --> 00:44:28,348
♪ Here's a heart
that's always faithful ♪

627
00:44:28,567 --> 00:44:32,691
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

628
00:44:34,287 --> 00:44:40,222
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

629
00:44:40,885 --> 00:44:44,402
♪ To you alone ♪

630
00:44:44,566 --> 00:44:50,372
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

631
00:44:50,619 --> 00:44:56,652
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

632
00:44:57,180 --> 00:44:59,631
♪ Whatever you want ♪

633
00:45:00,128 --> 00:45:04,772
♪ Everything I've done ♪

634
00:45:05,109 --> 00:45:07,392
♪ What's it for? ♪

635
00:45:07,446 --> 00:45:12,910
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

636
00:45:13,339 --> 00:45:18,757
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

637
00:45:19,154 --> 00:45:24,652
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

638
00:45:24,949 --> 00:45:30,712
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪
